1
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:46,720
Report!

2
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:49,560
Your Majesty, rebels have launched a surprise attack in the capital.

3
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:50,880
They are coming in full force.

4
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:51,720
What?

5
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,500
How could this happen?

6
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:58,240
This is too sudden.

7
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:01,520
Yue.

8
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,880
Go to Yan's palace first.

9
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:08,220
Please be careful.

10
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,280
You be careful too.

11
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:14,850
Don't worry.

12
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,680
Logically,

13
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:24,720
the Grand Princess has already been imprisoned.

14
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,250
Why are there still rebels?

15
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:29,280
I remember this game.

16
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:32,410
Different actions will trigger different storylines.

17
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:35,370
Maybe it was triggered accidentally.

18
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:37,160
What a crappy storyline.

19
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,880
It had to trigger during my wedding.

20
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,740
Couldn't it wait until I was done?

21
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:45,039
What's so good about this crappy wedding of yours?

22
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:53,120
I wonder where these rebels came from.

23
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,160
By the way, Jingyuan,

24
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:57,360
you joined this game earlier than I did.

25
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:59,280
Didn't you meet other players

26
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,500
to know the storyline in advance?

27
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,600
They usually die in the first level.

28
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:10,680
It was in the second episode where you met Si Xingxuan.

29
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:15,160
But Si Xingxuan wouldn't kill anyone.

30
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,520
But Eunuch Sun could.

31
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,280
Otherwise, how do you think

32
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:21,200
he got the title of tyrant?

33
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:30,980
What's that smell?

34
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,560
Oh no.

35
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,770
Enduring hardships for ten years,

36
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:56,040
I have finally waited for this day.

37
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,640
Fan Ying?

38
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:09,240
Aren't you Si Xinglan's male favorite?

39
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,320
Why are you here?

40
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,400
What are you going to do?

41
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,360
You killed my Lan'er,

42
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,520
so of course I am here to avenge her.

43
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,720
Avenge?

44
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:24,040
How about you wait a few days

45
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,480
until Si Xingxuan and I get married?

46
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,760
Are you okay?

47
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,840
To tell you the truth,

48
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,360
I was the youngest and most promising

49
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,200
high priest of the Ancient Wu Tribe,

50
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,600
with a boundless future.

51
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:37,040
Donglin wiped out my entire tribe,

52
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:40,040
forcing me to become a male favorite.

53
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:42,000
I could only hide beside Si Xinglan,

54
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,600
helping her refine Gu poison.

55
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,440
I did it all so that this world

56
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:47,880
would become the world of my Ancient Wu Tribe.

57
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:52,320
So you were the one who poisoned Xingyao and Axuan with Gu.

58
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,240
That's right.

59
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:57,840
If that fool Si Xinglan hadn't forced the emperor to abdicate without permission,

60
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,160
ruining my years of planning,

61
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,690
I would have been the emperor long ago.

62
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,340
What are you guys playing?

63
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:08,360
Untie me quickly.

64
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,520
I need to pee.

65
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,320
Shut up!

66
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:15,080
What can you do by tying us up?

67
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,279
You can't defeat him.

68
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,600
Now you've fallen into my

69
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,400
trap of luring the tiger out of the mountain.

70
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,280
With the three of you held here,

71
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:27,840
Si Xingxuan will definitely come to rescue you.

72
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,760
If he enters this palace,

73
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:32,480
he will surely become a rat in a trap,

74
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,640
at my mercy.

75
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,840
Lord Fan, Si Xingxuan and his troops

76
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,900
were stopped by us at the palace gate.

77
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,920
He's finally here.

78
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,080
Brother.

79
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:19,180
Trying to rescue them single-handedly.

80
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,000
Playing the hero.

81
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,000
Kill!

82
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:51,159
I want to see how long you can last.

83
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,450
Still won't surrender?

84
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,720
Si Xingxuan.

85
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,160
You hid it well.

86
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,920
Good martial arts.

87
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,480
Good.

88
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,570
It's good that you're here.

89
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,010
Let the three of them go.

90
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,760
Wait, why?

91
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:36,400
Since Si Xingxuan is here,

92
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,440
our goal is achieved.

93
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:40,840
We only have a grudge against the Donglin royal family.

94
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:42,280
We can't kill the innocent.

95
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:42,940
Let them go.

96
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,440
Then what about that prince?

97
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,600
Isn't he also a member of the royal family?

98
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,480
Why let him go?

99
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,159
He's just a fool.

100
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:50,040
You're the fool.

101
00:06:59,200 --> 00:06:59,800
Watch out!

102
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,480
Yuanyuan!

103
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:16,440
Jingyuan!

104
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:19,440
Yuanyuan, what's wrong with you?

105
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,160
You're bleeding!

106
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,000
Yuanyuan!

107
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:23,760
Yuanyuan,

108
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,760
you're bleeding.

109
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,040
A'yan, I'm fine.

110
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,520
No, no.

111
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:32,760
A'yan,

112
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:37,000
I won't be able to take care of you anymore.

113
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,800
No, no.

114
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:41,200
A'yan, from now on, in this world,

115
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,600
you must

116
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,320
take good care of yourself.

117
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:48,920
No, no.

118
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:53,640
Brother Yuanyuan, Brother Jingyuan!

119
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,480
Jingyuan, don't leave me.

120
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:59,400
Please don't leave me.

121
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,200
Since you managed to break into the palace,

122
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,659
I want to see exactly what you are capable of.

123
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:43,480
Stand down.

124
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,960
So many brothers died today.

125
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,760
I will settle this with him alone.

126
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:54,520
Alright.

127
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,400
I will oblige you.
